      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R2 used under documented QMS with ISO 9001 certification; solver validation suite results on file.",
      "rationale": "The FEA platform (Ansys Mechanical 2023 R2) is deployed under a documented quality management system. Vendor-supplied verification suite results are archived and traceable to the analysis record. Required gradation 2 achieved."
